# ── redaction firewall ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Raw, unsanitized pulls from private repos land here and must NEVER be
# committed. Only reviewed, sanitized content is promoted into src/content.
.private/
scripts/.cache/
src/data/snapshots/**/raw/
*.raw.json
*.unsanitized.*

# local-only handoff notes and dev logs (not part of the published site)
HANDOFF.md
dev.log

# private planning documents and local agent/session config — never publish
Product Lifecycle Showcase Spec for Lichtspiel and Windchime.md
.claude/
